subject: Basketball
College Athletics
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Fifth-ranked Syracuse defeated Stanford on Friday night in the championship game of the N.I.T. Season Tip-Off at Madison Square Garden while Harvard beat No. 22 Florida State.
